summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 221E, Page 8 of the Official Zoning map of The City of Seattle Ordinance 86300, to rezone certain property in Block 9, Seattle Suburban Home Tracts from Single, Family Residence Medium Density (RS 7200) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone, and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith. (C.F. 288960, Petition of Russell Nelson).
